## Summary
This documentation explains how to implement SuperTokens tenant discovery functionality using plugins for React and NodeJS SDKs, which automatically routes users to appropriate tenants based on email domain extraction (e.g., user@company.com routes to 'company' tenant) with fallback to 'public' tenant for popular email providers.

